## Constraints

- Do NOT write any code. This is planning only.
- Every behavior must be testable through a public interface (seam).
- Every behavior must reference a `spec_id` from the specification system.
- If no spec data was provided, you must use `spec/goal/capture` to create a specification before listing behaviors.
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Preserve the original prompt structure and formatting.
- Handle missing variables gracefully (leave as-is or use default if specified).

